qas.question: Exercise-induced bronchoconstriction is common in what profession?
What professions has the highest rate of Exercise-induced bronchoconstriction?

answers.text: cyclists (up to 45%), swimmers, and cross-country skiers

qas.question: What conditions are more likely to cause Exercise-induced bronchoconstriction?

answers.text: when it is dry and cold
